<HEADLINE>
<P>
PANAMA, CHINA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding Panama: Too much, too late. 
</P>
<P>
Regarding China: Too much, too soon. 
</P>
<P>
RICHARD SINSHEIMER 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills 
</P>
