DEFICIENCY SYNDROME; GOVERNMENT REGULATION; INFECTIONS; HOSPITALS; NURSES; 
DOCTORS; OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ADMINISTRATION; TESTIMONY; HEPATITIS B; 
