the Assembly chamber for his last State of the State address. Looking on are 
Assembly Speaker Willie Brown, left, and Senate President Pro Tem David 
Roberti. LARRY DAVIS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Southland Edition) Gov. 
George Deukmejian: "The California that was once headed for the poorhouse is 
now an economic powerhouse." MICHAEL EDWARDS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
