<P>
MGM/UA No Longer for Sale: Jeffrey C. Barbakow, chairman, president and chief 
executive of MGM/UA Communications Co., said the studio, which had been on the 
verge of being sold last year, will no longer be actively seeking a buyer. 
</P>
