ANA (CA) -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; HIGH RISE BUILDINGS; TRANSIT SYSTEMS 
-- ORANGE COUNTY; SHIMIZU AMERICA CORP; ORIENT CORP 
</P>
