<P>
Katella 47, Los Alamitos 46 -- With seven seconds to play, Ruth Harker stole 
the ball and made a layup to give Katella the victory at Los Alamitos. Allison 
Arredondo led all scorers with 25 points for Los Alamitos (0-2, 4-10). Margaret 
Harker scored 16 for Katella (5-9, 1-1). 
</P>
