<P>
Tustin 58, University 53 -- Christine Garner had 26 points and Wanda Sequeira 
had 17, including nine in the fourth quarter for host Tustin (12-5, 1-0). 
University's Denise Gandara had 26 points despite being double-teamed most of 
the game. She also had nine rebounds. University is 10-4, 0-1. 
</P>
<P>
Saddleback 35, Estancia 33 -- Janet Chacon scored with 17 seconds left to break 
a 33-33 tie for visiting Saddleback (6-7, 1-0). Chacon led Saddleback with 14 
points. Priscilla Sarmiento added 11 for Saddleback. 
</P>
<P>
Newport Harbor 44, Corona del Mar 33 -- Forward Stacey Giem scored 28 points to 
lead host Newport Harbor (5-7, 1-0). Giem scored four points in the first 
quarter, eight in the second, six in the third and 10 in the fourth. 
</P>
</TEXT>
