<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Randy Tincher has been named to the newly created position of area vice 
president for Carl's Jr. 
</P>
<P>
Restaurants in Southern California. He will head operations for 281 
company-owned restaurants in Southern California. Tincher, who joined the 
company in 1976, had most recently been director of operations for Orange 
County. Carl's Jr. Restaurants are owned or franchised by Carl Karcher 
Enterprises, based in Anaheim. 
</P>
